Ataxia Game Engine

First, install Go. Ataxia runs best on the current weekly release. See: http://golang.org/doc/install.html

$ hg clone -r weekly https://go.googlecode.com/hg/ go
$ cd go/src
$ ./all.bash

You will need to install GoLUA from https://github.com/xenith-studios/golua

Once Go and GoLUA are installed:

$ make deppkg
$ make

Modify etc/config.lua

Run Ataxia:

$ ./bin/ataxia
